{"tid":906977,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★賀！內地中小企難捱　傳二線手機品牌金立已停產","createTime":"2018-11-18T12:20:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T12:34:25.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a04e7c82e9b2fe083190bbcc3255206a2587d8b7","tid":906977,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T12:20:34.000Z","msg":"內地傳媒報道，內地二線手機品牌金立在東莞的廠區幾天前陷入「停工狀態」；而在今年4月時，該公司亦因資金問題，有約一半東莞廠區員工離職。<br />\n<br />\n據研究公司GFK的數據顯示，去年智能手機品牌在中國銷售量中，金立排名第七，共售出1,494萬部；而該公司去年在印度的市佔率亦排名第六。然而，在今年初起金立傳陷財困，並宣布會減少東莞工廠約一半人手。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述金立內部員工指出，今年初起，金立的產品在工廠內已停產，只剩下代工生產部分仍在運作。<br />\n<br />\n該員工指，今年上半年，東莞金立工廠主要為當地的塑膠模具及電子科技代工。在這段時間內，工人的開工率基本飽和，但代工費用很低。<br />\n<br />\n但在6月之後，東莞金立工廠已「無事可做」，在接下來的數月工人上班往往就是打卡，待上8個小時便下班了；廠區的員工人數亦由2,000人降至現在的300人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181118/bkn-20181118182213750-1118_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20181118%2Fbkn-20181118182213750-1118_00842_001.html&d=uLyCpjOYDpSsspcmNYPH%2BcP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=f2b6e334\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181118/bkn-20181118182213750-1118_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"53a3aa49e07ba0567fe18b7a75d748c64e6023ed","tid":906977,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T12:20:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又贏"},{"pid":"7dd6ac0f7476a1274b11679ca8038480c1c2c881","tid":906977,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T12:21:45.000Z","msg":"可以返鄉下了"},{"pid":"256b6165dc9e1f9d5b3be2d24b9db738700c4a4c","tid":906977,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T12:22:22.000Z","msg":"未聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbc1f2090650312b53abf98934488edd0a6ab9cd","tid":906977,"uid":31946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T12:23:55.000Z","msg":"又多一班人可以下鄉搞生意創新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"215d7c03b10414d58a9a74edf8883f791b06ce62","tid":906977,"uid":68097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T12:26:09.000Z","msg":"又多一班農業新力軍，厲害了"},{"pid":"fe3bd449d58bb0dae4c93b25ab9695a66e59ce69","tid":906977,"uid":187554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"256b6165dc9e1f9d5b3be2d24b9db738700c4a4c","tid":906977,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T12:22:22.000Z","msg":"未聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T12:27:37.000Z","msg":"正常啦 佢地由抄人地手機開始做<br />\n代工開始做 做到品牌轉型<br />\n但係轉極出問題"},{"pid":"f0ab6884536aac41a695025dce774024bc31f437","tid":906977,"uid":32675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T12:30:42.000Z","msg":"又有幾千人回鄉創業,形勢一片大好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15efd696dcdfc6d5bec1d4454241910cc4714502","tid":906977,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T12:32:16.000Z","msg":"呢個? gionee<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gionee.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gionee.com%2F&d=uLyCpjOYDpSsspcmNYPH%2BcP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=671d7f62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gionee.com/</a>"},{"pid":"ab4d1c8f831b0477579ce4e8543eafbd11f25744","tid":906977,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T12:34:25.000Z","msg":"以為死咗好耐"}]}